Articles.Content:
Well, if you want them lighter, you can always reduce the weight.

Here's a module manager cfg that should halve their weight:

    @PART[fairingSize1]{  @MODULE[ModuleProceduralFairing]  {	  @UnitAreaMass = 0.015  }}@PART[fairingSize2]{  @MODULE[ModuleProceduralFairing]  {	  @UnitAreaMass = 0.02  }}@PART[fairingSize3]{  @MODULE[ModuleProceduralFairing]  {	  @UnitAreaMass = 0.03  }}
